Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Travel myths
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b03z8hry
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 22 Jun 1975
Travel expectations very rarely live up to the reality. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.